sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_snc_nice_iex.IEX</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Single Outbound webservice, all other methods pass params and function names into it.</description><name>IEX</name><script><![CDATA[IEX = {
	field_map: {
		'schedule': {
			'agent_id': {
				iex: getProperty('schedule.agent_id','agentOID'),
				sn: 'u_agent_oid'
			},
			'activity_id': {
				iex: getProperty('schedule.activity_id','actCodeOID')
			},
			'start_date_time': {
				iex: getProperty('schedule.start_date_time','startDateTime'),
				sn: 'start_date_time'
			},
			'end_date_time': {
				iex: getProperty('schedule.end_date_time','endDateTime'),
				sn: 'end_date_time'
			}
		},
		'activity_code': {
			'id': {
				iex: getProperty('activity_code.id','oid'),
				sn: 'id'
			},
			'icon': {
				iex: getProperty('activity_code.icon','actCodeIconOID'),
				sn: 'icon_id'
			},
			'name': {
				iex: getProperty('activity_code.name','name'),
				sn: 'name'
			}
		}
	},
	authenticate : function(){
		var isAuth = authenticate();
		while(!isAuth){
			isAuth = authenticate();
		}
		return isAuth;
	},
	logout : function(){
		var response = send("AuthenticationServiceImplService","logout",true);
		if(response){
			var status = response.getStatusCode();
			//log("STATUS:\t" + status + "\nBODY:\t" + response.getBody().toString());
			if(status == 200){
				setSession("");
			}
		}
		return true;
	},
	ping : function(){
		var response = send("AuthenticationServiceImplService","ping",true);
		return response;
	},
	
	// TODO map fields?
	getUserDetails : function(internalIDs, tenantID, businessEntityID){
		var response = send("UUATotalviewSubSysWebServiceService","getUserDetails",true,{
			InternalIDs : internalIDs,
			BusinessEntityID : businessEntityID,
			TenantID : tenantID
		});
		return response;
	},
	getChangedUsers : function(dateTime){
		var response = send("UUATotalviewSubSysWebServiceService","getChangedUsers",true,{
			DateTime : dateTime
		});
		return response;
	},
	getMUs : function(){
		var response = send("CustomerResourcesServiceImplService","getMUs",true);
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	getActivityCodes : function(){
		var response = send("CustomerResourcesServiceImplService","getActivityCodes",true);
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	getAllTimeZones : function(){
		var response = send("CustomerResourcesServiceImplService","getAllTimeZones",true);
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	getWFMSkills : function(){
		var response = send("CustomerResourcesServiceImplService","getWFMSkills",true);
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	
	// TODO map fields
	getAgentsForMUs : function(muOIDs, startDate, endDate){
		var muOIDsQuery = getXMLQuery(muOIDs,"muOIDs");
		var response = send("MUResourcesServiceImplService","getAgentsForMUs",true, {
			muOIDs : muOIDsQuery,
			startDate : startDate,
			endDate : endDate
		});
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	
	
	/*
	Overall performance per MU not what we are looking for
	getPerformanceDataForMU : function(muOID, startDateTime, endDateTime){
		var response = send("MUResourcesServiceImplService","getPerformanceDataForMU",true,{
			muOID : muOID,
			startDateTime : startDateTime,
			endDateTime : endDateTime
		});
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	getPerformanceDataForMuByCt : function(muOID, startDateTime, endDateTime){
		var response = send("MUResourcesServiceImplService","getPerformanceDataForMuByCt",true,{
			muOID : muOID,
			startDateTime : startDateTime,
			endDateTime : endDateTime
		});

		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	*/
	
	/*
	Currently not supported by API
	insertScheduleActivityForAgents : function(agtScheduleOIDs, actCodeOID, startDateTime, endDateTime){
		var agtScheduleOIDsQuery = getXMLQuery(agtScheduleOIDs, "agtScheduleOIDs");
		var response = send("AgentResourcesServiceImplService","insertScheduleActivityForAgents",true,{
			agtScheduleOIDs : agtScheduleOIDsQuery,
			actCodeOID : actCodeOID,
			startDateTime : startDateTime,
			endDateTime : endDateTime
		});
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	modifyScheduleActivitiesForAgents : function(agentSchedules, scheduleActivities){
		var response = send("AgentResourcesServiceImplService","modifyScheduleActivitiesForAgents",true);
	},
	deleteScheduleActivityForAgents : function(agtScheduleOIDs, actCodeOID, startDateTime, endDateTime){
		var agtScheduleOIDsQuery = getXMLQuery(agtScheduleOIDs, "agtScheduleOIDs");
		var response = send("AgentResourcesServiceImplService","deleteScheduleActivityForAgents",true, {
			agtScheduleOIDs : agtScheduleOIDsQuery,
			actCodeOID : actCodeOID,
			startDateTime : startDateTime,
			endDateTime : endDateTime
		});
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	*/
	
	// TODO map fields
	getStaffingTablesForMu : function(muID, startDate, endDate){
		var response = send("PlannerResourcesServiceService","getStaffingTablesForMu",true,{
			muID : muID,
			startDate : startDate,
			endDate : endDate
		});
		return response;
	},
	getUserSchedule : function(startGDT, endGDT, userID){
		userID = userID || gs.getUserID();
		var localAgentIDField = this.field_map.schedule.agent_id.sn;
		var userGR = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
		userGR.addQuery("sys_id",userID);
		userGR.addNotNullQuery(localAgentIDField);
		userGR.query();
		if(userGR.next()){
			return this.getAgentSchedules([userGR[localAgentIDField].toString()],startGDT,endGDT);
		}
		return false;
	},
	getAgentSchedules : function(agentIDs, startGDT, endGDT){
		var remoteAgentIDField = this.field_map.schedule.agent_id.iex;
		var startDate = getFormattedDate(startGDT);
		var endDate = getFormattedDate(endGDT);
		var agentIDsQuery = getXMLQuery(agentIDs, remoteAgentIDField+'s');
		var resData = {
			startDate : startDate,
			endDate : endDate
		};
		resData[remoteAgentIDField+'s'] = agentIDsQuery;
		var response = send("AgentResourcesServiceImplService","getAgentSchedules", true, resData);
		return getResponseArray(response);
	},
	getAgentsSkills : function(agentIDs, startGDT, endGDT){
		var remoteAgentIDField = this.field_map.schedule.agent_id.iex;
		var startDate = getFormattedDate(startGDT);
		var endDate = getFormattedDate(endGDT);
		var agentIDsQuery = getXMLQuery(agentIDs, remoteAgentIDField+'s');
		var resData = {
			startDate : startDate,
			endDate : endDate
		};
		resData[remoteAgentIDField+'s'] = agentIDsQuery;
		var response = send("AgentResourcesServiceImplService", "getAgentsSkills", true, resData);
	},
	
	// TODO replace table
	importMUs : function(data){
		upsertRecords("x_snc_sp_workspace_iex_mu_import", data);
	},
	importActivityCodes: function(data, table){
		var activityIDField = this.field_map.activity_code.id.iex;
		var transformMap = {};
		for (var x in this.field_map.activity_code) {
			transformMap[this.field_map.activity_code[x].iex] = this.field_map.activity_code[x].sn;
		}
		upsertRecords(table, data, activityIDField, transformMap);
	},
	
	// TODO replace table
	importTimeZones : function(data){
		//x_snc_sp_workspace_iex_timezone
		for(var i = 0; i != data.length; i++){
			var current = data[i];
			upsertRecord("x_snc_sp_workspace_iex_timezone",{"name":current},"name");
		}
	},
	
	// TODO replace table - difference?
	importWFMSkills : function(data){
		//x_snc_sp_workspace_iex_skill
		upsertRecords("x_snc_sp_workspace_iex_skill",data,"skillOID");
	},
	importAgentsSchedules : function(data, startGDT, endGDT, testing){
		var remoteAgentIDField = this.field_map.schedule.agent_id.iex;
		var localAgentIDField = this.field_map.schedule.agent_id.sn;
		var remoteActivityCodeField = this.field_map.schedule.activity_id.iex;
		var returnArray = [];
		data = Array.isArray(data) ? data : [data];
		for(var i = 0; i != data.length; i++){
			var firstLayer = data[i];
			var agentID = firstLayer[remoteAgentIDField].toString();
			var baseSchedule = Array.isArray(firstLayer.baseSchedule) ? firstLayer.baseSchedule : [firstLayer.baseSchedule];
			var user = getUser(agentID, localAgentIDField);
			var userSchedule;
			if (testing) {
				userSchedule = getTestUserScheduleID(user);
			} else {
				userSchedule = getUserScheduleID(user);
				removeScheduledEvents(userSchedule, startGDT, endGDT);
			}
			for(var x = 0; x != baseSchedule.length; x++){
				var schedule = baseSchedule[x];
				var events = schedule.scheduleDetail;
				events = Array.isArray(events) ? events : [events];
				for(var z = 0; z != events.length; z++){
					var event = events[z];
					if(event){
						var activityName = event[remoteActivityCodeField] ? getActivityCode(event[remoteActivityCodeField].toString(), 'x_snc_nice_iex_activity_code', 'id') : "";
						var eventStartGDT = new GlideDateTime();
						var eventEndGDT = new GlideDateTime();
						eventStartGDT.setValueUTC(event.startDateTime,"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm");
						eventEndGDT.setValueUTC(event.endDateTime,"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm");
						if(startGDT.before(eventStartGDT) && endGDT.after(eventStartGDT) && startGDT.before(eventEndGDT) && endGDT.after(eventEndGDT)){
							returnArray.push(addScheduledEvent(userSchedule, activityName, eventStartGDT, eventEndGDT));
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		return returnArray;
	},
	getFormattedDateTime:getFormattedDateTime,
	getFormattedDate:getFormattedDate,
	log:log,
	logJSON : logJSON
};
function getActivityCode(activityCodeID, activityCodeTable, activityCodeIDField){
	var activityCodeGR = new GlideRecord(activityCodeTable);
	if(activityCodeGR.get(activityCodeIDField,activityCodeID)){
		return activityCodeGR.name.toString();
	}
	return activityCodeID;
}	
function getUserScheduleID(user){
	var userScheduleGR = new GlideRecord("agent_events");
	userScheduleGR.addQuery("user",user.sys_id.toString());
	userScheduleGR.addQuery("personal_schedule.sys_scope",this.scope_id);
	userScheduleGR.query();
	if(!userScheduleGR.hasNext()){
		var scheduleGR = new GlideRecord("cmn_schedule");
		scheduleGR.initialize();
		scheduleGR.name = user.getDisplayValue() + " Schedule";
		scheduleGR.sys_scope = this.scope_id;
		scheduleGR.time_zone = "GMT";
		scheduleGR.insert();

		userScheduleGR.initialize();
		userScheduleGR.user = user.sys_id.toString();
		userScheduleGR.personal_schedule = scheduleGR.sys_id.toString();
		userScheduleGR.insert();
	}else{
		userScheduleGR.next();
	}
	return userScheduleGR.personal_schedule.sys_id.toString();
}
function getTestUserScheduleID(user){
	var scheduleGR = new GlideRecord("cmn_schedule");
	scheduleGR.initialize();
	scheduleGR.name = user.getDisplayValue() + " Test Schedule";
	scheduleGR.time_zone = "GMT";
	var scheduleID =  scheduleGR.insert();
	var otherScheduleGR = new GlideRecord('cmn_other_schedule');
	otherScheduleGR.initialize();
	otherScheduleGR.schedule = "baf89f5edb903380604c9e7aca961955"; // testing schedule
	otherScheduleGR.child_schedule = scheduleID;
	otherScheduleGR.insert();
	return scheduleID;
}
function addScheduledEvent(scheduleID, name, startGDT, endGDT){
	if(startGDT.before(endGDT)){
		var spanGR = new GlideRecord("cmn_schedule_span");
		spanGR.initialize();
		spanGR.schedule = scheduleID;
		spanGR.start_date_time = new GlideScheduleDateTime(startGDT);
		spanGR.end_date_time = new GlideScheduleDateTime(endGDT);
		spanGR.name = name;
		spanGR.insert();
		return spanGR;
	}
	return {
		name : name,
		start : startGDT.getDisplayValue(),
		end : endGDT.getDisplayValue()
	};
}
function removeScheduledEvents(scheduleID, startGDT, endGDT){
	var startDT = getFormattedDateTime(startGDT);//.getDate().getByFormat("yyyyMMdd") + "T000000";
	var endDT = getFormattedDateTime(endGDT);//.getDate().getByFormat("yyyyMMdd") + "T235959";
	var spanGR = new GlideRecord("cmn_schedule_span");
	spanGR.addQuery("schedule",scheduleID);
	spanGR.addQuery("start_date_time",">=",startDT);
	spanGR.addQuery("end_date_time","<=",endDT);
	spanGR.deleteMultiple();
}
function getUser(agentID, localAgentIDField){

	}
	return false;

}
function getXMLQuery(valArray, xmlTag){
	var queryXML = "";

	}
	return queryXML;
}
function upsertRecords(tableName, dataSet, coalesceField, transformMap){
	for(var i = 0; i != dataSet.length; i++){
		if (transformMap) {
			upsertRecordWithTransform(tableName,dataSet[i],coalesceField,transformMap);
		} else {
			upsertRecord(tableName,dataSet[i],coalesceField);
		}
	}
}
function upsertRecord(tableName, data, coalesceField){
	var recordGR = new GlideRecord(tableName);
	var keys = Object.keys(data);
	var func = "insert";
	if(coalesceField){
		recordGR.addQuery(coalesceField.toLowerCase(), data[coalesceField].toString());
		recordGR.query();
		if(recordGR.hasNext()){
			recordGR.next();
			func = "update";
		}else{
			recordGR.initialize();
		}
	}else{
		recordGR.initialize();
	}
	for(var i = 0; i != keys.length; i++){
		var key = keys[i];
		var fieldName = (coalesceField ? key : "u_" + key).toLowerCase();
		recordGR.setValue(fieldName, data[key].toString());
	}
	recordGR[func]();
}
function upsertRecordWithTransform(tableName, data, coalesceField, transformMap){
	var recordGR = new GlideRecord(tableName);
	var fields = Object.keys(transformMap);
	var remoteCoalesceField = transformMap[coalesceField];
	var keys = Object.keys(data);
	var func = "insert";
	if(coalesceField){
		recordGR.addQuery(coalesceField, remoteCoalesceField);
		recordGR.query();
		if(recordGR.hasNext()){
			recordGR.next();
			func = "update";
		}else{
			recordGR.initialize();
		}
	}else{
		recordGR.initialize();
	}
	for(var i = 0; i != keys.length; i++){
		var key = keys[i];
		if (fields.indexOf(key) > -1) {
			recordGR.setValue(transformMap[key], data[key].toString());
		}
	}
	recordGR[func]();
}
function getResponseArray(response){
	var responseArray = [];
	if(response){
		var body = response.getBody();
		var xmlDoc = new XMLDocument2();
		xmlDoc.parseXML(body.toString());
		var node = xmlDoc.getDocumentElement().getFirstChild().getFirstChild();
		var nodeName = node.getNodeName();
		var jsonBody = gs.xmlToJSON(node.toString());
		responseArray = jsonBody[nodeName]["return"] ? jsonBody[nodeName]["return"] : [];
	}
	return responseArray;
}
function authenticate(){
	var response = send("AuthenticationServiceImplService","authenticate",false,{
		"authenticate.userLogonID":getProperty("username"),
		"authenticate.userLogonPWD":getProperty("password"),
		"authenticate.customerName":getProperty("customer_name")
	});
	if(response){
		var session = response.getHeader("Set-Cookie").toString().split(";")[0];
		if(session){
			setSession(session);
			return session;
		}
	}
	return false;
}
function send (soapService, soapFunction, requiresAuth, parameters){
	try{
		var soapMessage = new sn_ws.SOAPMessageV2("global." + soapService, soapFunction);
		if(getProperty("production").toString() == "true"){
			var endpoint = soapMessage.getEndpoint();
			endpoint = endpoint.replace("iex-ess-stage","iex-ess");
			soapMessage.setEndpoint(endpoint);
		}
		soapMessage.setMIDServer(getProperty("mid_server"));
		soapMessage.setEccParameter('skip_sensor', true);
		if(requiresAuth){
			var session = getSession();
			if(!session){
				return false;
			}
			soapMessage.setRequestHeader("Cookie", session);
		}
		if(parameters){
			var keys = Object.keys(parameters);
			for(var i = 0; i != keys.length; i++){
				var key = keys[i];
				var value = parameters[key].value || parameters[key];
				var setFunction = "setStringParameter" + (parameters[key].escape ? "" : "NoEscape");
				soapMessage[setFunction](key, value);
			}
		}
		var response = soapMessage.execute();
		var status = response.getStatusCode();
		var logMessage = "FUNCTION\t:\t" + soapFunction + "\n";
		logMessage += "STATUS\t\t:\t" + status + "\n";
		logMessage += "ENDPOINT\t:\t" + soapMessage.getEndpoint().toString() + "\n";
		logMessage += "REQUESTBODY\t:\t" + soapMessage.getRequestBody().toString() + "\n";
		logMessage += "REQUESTHEADERS\t:\t" + JSON.stringify(soapMessage.getRequestHeaders(),null,0) + "\n";
		logMessage += "RESPONSEBODY\t:\t"+ response.getBody();
		log(logMessage);
		if(status != 200){
			return false;
		}
		return response;
	}catch(ex){
		log("CATCH:\t" + ex.message);
	}
	return false;
}
function getSession(){
	var session = getProperty("session_id", false);
	if(session){
		return session;
	}else{
		return authenticate();
	}
}
function setSession(session){
	setProperty("session_id",session);
}
function log(message){
	if(getProperty("logging")){
		var gdt = new GlideDateTime();
		gs.info(gdt.getNumericValue() + "\n" + message.toString() + "\n");
	}
}
function logJSON(messageObject, spaces){
	spaces = spaces || 0;
	log(JSON.stringify(messageObject,null,spaces));
}
function getProperty(postfix, alternate){
	var prefix = "x_snc_nice_iex.iex";
	return gs.getProperty(prefix + "." + postfix, alternate || false);
}

function setProperty(postfix, value){
	var prefix = "x_snc_nice_iex.iex";
	gs.setProperty(prefix + "." + postfix, value);
}
function getFormattedDate(gdt){
	var year = gdt.getYearUTC();
	var month = gdt.getMonthUTC();
	var day = gdt.getDayOfMonthUTC();

	month = month < 10 ? "0" + month : month + "";
	day = day < 10 ? "0" + day : day + "";

	return year + "-" + month + "-" + day;//YYYY-MM-ddyear + month + day + "T" + hours + minutes + seconds;
}
function getFormattedDateTime(gdt){
	var year = gdt.getYearUTC();
	var month = gdt.getMonthUTC();
	var day = gdt.getDayOfMonthUTC();
	var dstOffset = gdt.getDSTOffset()/1000/60/60;
	var time = gdt.getTime();
	var hours = time.getHourOfDayUTC() + dstOffset;
	var minutes = time.getMinutesUTC();
	var seconds = time.getSeconds();

	month = month < 10 ? "0" + month : month + "";
	day = day < 10 ? "0" + day : day + "";
	hours = hours < 10 ? "0" + hours : hours + "";
	minutes = minutes < 10 ? "0" + minutes : minutes + "";
	seconds = seconds < 10 ? "0" + seconds : seconds + "";

	return year + month + day + "T" + hours + minutes + seconds;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jacob</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-21 13:45:32</sys_created_on><sys_id>9418a14adb90ff40604c9e7aca961992</sys_id><sys_mod_count>34</sys_mod_count><sys_name>IEX</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NICE IEX Spoke" source="x_snc_nice_iex">3ccaddcedb50ff40604c9e7aca96194f</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="NICE IEX Spoke">3ccaddcedb50ff40604c9e7aca96194f</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_9418a14adb90ff40604c9e7aca961992</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jacob</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-23 03:02:32</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
